msgid "Using the Charcoal filter"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#. +> trunk5
#: editor-filters-charcoal.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two sliders to control the effect on a scale of 1-100. The upper slider selects the pencil size, whereas the second slider adjusts the contrast (smoothness)."
msgstr ""

